name: Rocket-Leap
description:
***NEW UPDATE*** 19/12/2018

  • Fixed the respawn point for the Rocket.
  • Added 2 lives to each level, which means 5 in total in each level.
  • Added background music

...Let's see if you can go through the 10 levels of hell...

You are a rocket trying to fly throught obstacles and the hardships (pun intended), let's see if YOU can do it, I as the developer could'nt finish it lol 

Enjoy, and let me know what you think of the game in the comments below! 

Good/Bad feedback is always appreciated.

Donations aren't needed but always appreciated and motivates me to make more and better games!
